 What Where Find Jobs Advanced Job Search BRIM CI Consultant Capgemini 8,227 reviews Atlanta, GA 30328 Capgemini 8,227 reviews Read what people are saying about working here. Job details Job Type Contract Full Job Description Duration:  6+ months
 
 Requirement: 
1. 6 - 8 years of experience with Hands-on experience across SAP Convergent Invoicing implementation knowledge and FICA. Also having end to end knowledge of BRIM functional processes and data flows.
 
2. At least worked on 2 projects in BRIM CI/FICA area. Having knowledge of usage based and recurring billing scenarios.
 
3. Knowledge of Convergent Invoicing including BITs, CITs, Billing, Invoicing, Posting Area, Bill Cycle, FICA posting, Revenue Accrual, Billing Request, Invoicing offsetting etc.
 
4. Some knowledge of FICA configuration including FICA document configuration, Posting Area, clearing variant & rules, Inbound/outbound payment handling, Bank integration, write off, G/L Posting etc.
 
5. Good to have BRIM certification.
 
